        {
            "title": "A股半日收升   滬股升近0.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日報升，惟升幅遜外圍，兩市成交合計19126.49億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日升20點或0.49%，報4160點，今早以4150點開市，升10點或0.25%，最低見4138點，跌1點或0.02%，尾段升幅擴大，最高見4161點，升22點或0.53%，半日成交8685.73億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日升12點或0.09%，報14342點，今早開市報14371點，亦升42點或0.29%，早段見14382點，升53點或0.37%，為半日高位，其後轉跌，上午大部份時間報跌，中段低見14234，跌95點或0.66%，為半日低位，半日成交10440.76億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日升22點或0.47%，報4727點，今早升19點或0.42%，開報4725點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日12點或0.37%，報3330點，今早開市報3359點，升17點或0.51%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15618488-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e8%bf%910-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 11:44:08",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
